as well as the Device Shadow Service, which I'll talk about shortly,

13
00:00:37.284 --> 00:00:39.141
and the Message Broker,

14
00:00:39.141 --> 00:00:43.553
which will allow us to manage the messages coming in and out of IoT devices,

15
00:00:43.553 --> 00:00:45.803
as well as the Rules Engine,

16
00:00:45.803 --> 00:00:48.510
which will allow us to do some things related to what happens

17
00:00:48.510 --> 00:00:52.587
when devices take specific actions or some messages trigger

18
00:00:52.587 --> 00:00:55.361
to some Message Broker topic.

19
00:00:55.361 --> 00:00:57.232
So don't worry that we've only talked about some of

20
00:00:57.232 --> 00:00:58.914
these things on the top level here,

