50
00:02:24.985 --> 00:02:25.804
and authorization,

51
00:02:25.804 --> 00:02:29.831
to being able to manage and onboard new IoT things and

52
00:02:29.831 --> 00:02:31.954
devices that are coming into our system,

53
00:02:31.954 --> 00:02:35.049
and also to clarify some of the terminology and concepts

54
00:02:35.049 --> 00:02:39.489
surrounding many of these different components of IoT.

55
00:02:39.489 --> 00:02:41.943
So hopefully you feel pretty confident about where you're at

56
00:02:41.943 --> 00:02:43.588
